Description:
You come to a large chamber full of spider eggs, here you can also see some hatchlings and a herder who is taking care of the place.

Some of the eggs look like they are about to hatch so you can't waste any more time.

Also, there is no way to advance without the herder and the spiders noticing your presence there, it seems that your only option is to fight.
DescriptionAction: You must decide how to approach this fight.
